title: Sai Sriram Uppada
text:
Hello everyone!!
I’m ’ Sai Sriram Uppada ‘, and I prefer to go by the name’ Ram ’, and I recently completed my undergraduate studies in Information Technology at Gayatri Vidya Parishad College Of Engineering (A), Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India in the year 2023. Currently, I’m filled with excitement as I embark on my master’s journey in data analytics engineering.
